sequenceDiagram
    participant CI as CI/CD Runner
    participant Extractor as model-extractor<br/>(Go CLI)
    participant FS as Local Filesystem
    participant RHReg as registry.redhat.io<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant AReg as registry.access.redhat.com<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant HF as huggingface.co<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Docker as Konflux Pipeline<br/>(Docker Build)
    participant Quay as quay.io/rhoai<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Container as Data Container<br/>(sleep infinity)
    participant Dashboard as RHOAI Dashboard

    Note over CI,HF: Flow 1: Model Catalog Generation (CI/CD Build Time)

    CI->>FS: Read models-index.yaml,<br/>validated-models-index.yaml,<br/>other-models-index.yaml
    FS-->>Extractor: Model definitions

    par Fetch OCI Metadata
        Extractor->>RHReg: GET /v2/{image}/manifests/{tag}<br/>TLS 1.2+, No Auth (public)
        RHReg-->>Extractor: OCI manifests<br/>(architectures, timestamps, layers)
    and Fetch HuggingFace Metadata
        Extractor->>HF: GET /api/models/{model_id}<br/>TLS 1.2+, Bearer Token (optional)
        HF-->>Extractor: Model details, README,<br/>collections, validated lists
    end

    Extractor->>Extractor: Merge metadata<br/>(7 priority levels,<br/>confidence-based override)
    Extractor->>FS: Write models-catalog.yaml,<br/>validated-models-catalog.yaml,<br/>other-models-catalog.yaml

    Note over CI,AReg: Flow 2: MCP Server Catalog Generation (CI/CD Build Time)

    CI->>FS: Read *-mcp-servers-index.yaml
    FS-->>Extractor: MCP server definitions
    Extractor->>FS: Read input/mcp_servers/*.yaml
    Extractor->>AReg: GET /v2/{image}/manifests/{tag}<br/>TLS 1.2+, No Auth (public)
    AReg-->>Extractor: MCP container metadata<br/>(architectures, timestamps)
    Extractor->>FS: Write redhat-mcp-servers-catalog.yaml,<br/>partner-mcp-servers-catalog.yaml,<br/>community-mcp-servers-catalog.yaml

    Note over Docker,Quay: Container Image Build & Push

    Docker->>FS: COPY data/*.yaml
    Docker->>Quay: Push image<br/>TLS 1.2+, Quay credentials
    Quay-->>Docker: Image pushed

    Note over Container,Dashboard: Flow 3: Runtime Data Consumption (On-Cluster)

    Container->>Container: sleep infinity<br/>(data-only, no binary)
    Dashboard->>Container: Volume mount /app/data
    Container-->>Dashboard: Catalog YAML files<br/>(shared filesystem)
